HEADWORD: re-insure
<hw>re-insure</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>to provide additional
insurance for.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> reinsure.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>to insure again by transferring to another insurance
company all or a part of a liability assumed.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> reinsure.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reinsure</ent>⟦br⟧
